OL,7,FIsolation, safety at work and
OL,8,Fspeaking out are some of the key
OL,9,Ffindings from a review into the
OL,10,Fculture at University Hospitals
OL,11,FBirmingham NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,13,FOne in 10 staff said they never felt
OL,14,Fsafe at work, while one in four said
OL,15,Fthey felt discriminated against and
OL,16,F53% felt bullied or harassed.
OL,18,FMany said they experienced a lack of
OL,19,Frespect, while others said they were
OL,20,Fnot confident in speaking up against
OL,21,Fpoor behaviour.
OL,3,CKey findings from report published
OL,4,Cinto bullying culture at University
OL,5,CHospitals Birmingham Trust
